description: This Chainlink VRF top 9% rating Chukcha purrs with a rating of 75, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 75, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Nine Lives for North, Leverage for East, Leverage for South, and 1 for West. Chukcha has the personality suit of quant. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/30751-96611-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Chukcha [75 Votes, Top 9% Rating]
